          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37027910/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37027910/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lutoss/" class=" " title="Lhvtsalgffcc ">Lhvtsalgffcc </a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37027910">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">那些聆听小孩的哭声并且了解其含义的人都将懂得，那里潜伏着各种心灵的力量，那是跟我们通常的想象截然不同的可怕力量，深深的愤怒，毁灭的痛苦和欲望。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-20 22:48</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
